Package: mmorpg-orchestrator
Version: __VERSION__
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: docker.io | docker-ce, docker-compose-plugin | docker-compose
Maintainer: Samuel <lordnns@example.com>
Homepage: https://github.com/Lordnns/MMORPG
Description: MMORPG lab — dedicated orchestrator VM
 Runs the orchestrator on a dedicated VM in remote-docker mode. Dispatches
 DS spawn/kill requests to fleet-ds hosts via their host_agent.
 .
 Configure /etc/default/mmorpg-orchestrator (REDIS_URL, DS_HOSTS,
 AGENT_TOKEN, ORCH_ADVERTISE_HOST), then:
   systemctl start mmorpg-orchestrator
